Comment: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個樸素的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.69,0:01:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 一六
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們學校會找個啥都不懂的傢伙來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.42,0:01:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指老師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了他還有誰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.14,0:01:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.47,0:01:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我覺得他很努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.78,0:01:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也在嘗試著去更加地了解我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.48,0:02:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 大家有沒有考慮過自己未來的主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.09,0:02:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有…考慮過一點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這和那個語文老師又沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.95,0:02:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說老師怎麼樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夏日祭典上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶然碰到了來學校教書前的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.17,0:02:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.93,0:02:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他端槍的姿勢非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有天我也能被他那樣拿著…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我的擊錘…我的擊錘要敲下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風子你真H
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.41,0:02:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:03:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕 探望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要寫到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道該寫什麼好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西你隨便寫寫就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.12,0:03:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看我寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:23.15,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.21,0:03:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼一點？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都怎麼寫的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:29.51,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:32.13,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.37,0:03:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我想得太多了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希格 我要去囉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊 芬子你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖和了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希格？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面這麼冷 她們還能玩得這麼開心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換做我的話都不敢想像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 年糕已經烤好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別躲在屋子裡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一六你也來跟我們玩滑雪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭冷天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 真沒勁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是沒勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連待著不動都很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼還要特地去坐著雪橇吹冷風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那玩這個如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雪天使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:26.20,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(254,358)}雪\N天\N使\N\N芬\N子\N之\N作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 看起來很像天使吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個遊戲在歐洲很有人氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希格做的更好看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:34.53,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1232,548)}希\N格\N之\N作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的自信之作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在寒冷的地方人 就只會玩那種玩意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼 希格
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三點射模式真是意外的弱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連區區的寒冷都沒法戰勝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這就是所謂的會叫的狗不咬人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:05:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希…希格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.31,0:06:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換做平常的話我就會這麼說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我是不會上你當的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想挑釁我 讓我和你們打雪仗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我給你們加些有利條件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.46,0:06:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然對不擅長遠射的一六和艾爾來說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場比賽就不公平了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是挺高興的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是單純啊 一六
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個 冷靜點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這群傢伙真有精力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師也要來玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是老樣子啊 喜歡亂射一通
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 先投降的人就輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你便
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我奉陪到底
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.73,0:06:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉到雪海下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.36,0:07:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個就是黃金搭檔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我要幹什麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快幫我做雪球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點的話 我就要變成單發模式啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會在那出現障礙物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師你為了救學生居然犧牲自我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是教師的典範啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對芬子做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還挺能幹的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從上面傳來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾爾 停下 停下 快停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的手指已經沒知覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明應該是很暖和的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我卻一點也感覺不到溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 腦袋一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候應該吃些東西恢複下體力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒體力去做吃的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們不介意 我可以幫你們做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.96,0:08:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 為什麼希格你沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是被製作成在-20℃下也能使用的槍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-20℃？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:11.93,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1228,295)}少\N女\N峰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:11.93,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Banner;20,{\fs52\fsp4\an2}伯爾尼阿爾卑斯山脈的山峰 海拔4158米。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在少女峰上使用的槍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能稱作是瑞士的突擊步槍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞士真神奇！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這些是小八的年糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因為那傢伙是日本出生的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一八的媽媽就送了很多來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會送到一六這來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說曹操曹操到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.79,0:09:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小八 在這在這
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們馬上要開火鍋派對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去 老家的特產
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.20,0:09:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:09:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔬菜呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希格 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是比利時的國旗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,番茄 奶酪 還有專為芬子準備的比利時巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 謝謝你 希格
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰把火鍋託給希格的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說我從一四姐那裡聽說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,語文老師帶了這麼大一個口罩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後去買了好多泡麵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來一個人過 很孤單呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是感冒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是那次打雪仗時得到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類真是麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:54.18,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(710,522)}輪不到你們來說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起去語文老師家裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去探病吧 探病
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 真令人意外
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一六居然會說出這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了個不錯的打發時間的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 老師他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什麼名字來著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫語文老師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是叫語文老師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,語文老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好冷好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 誰知道他住哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 就在我們宿舍的正後方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:38.32,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(457,441)}地獄坡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:38.32,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(974,281)}學生宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的最危險的地方最安全吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一六 那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:11:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總不能空著手去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實如此呢 去買些東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要買什麼價錢的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人兩百日元左右就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？艾爾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個窮姑娘就只在這種時候才逃得快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一六你啊 不要只拿桃子罐頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 橘子罐頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是感冒時必吃的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風子 風子 你看！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不懂幽默
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布丁？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 布丁很重要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G3學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.68,0:13:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了 我正想要好好的和你說一次話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:25.08,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz5.975\pos(580,512)}便宜！迅捷！貨品齊全！年末年始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.48,0:13:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希格不見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.90,0:13:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我們兩個人付錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 真是預想外的支出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零用錢已經沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為你買那麼多桃子罐頭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 我一定要讓他還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨居的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在房間裡找找的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.65,0:13:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總會有那麼一兩件不能被看到的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是探病哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是探病哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:14:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把一六帶去真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}那得有多少錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 教授
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這狗狗是誰家的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道嗎 教授從我們學校建校時就在了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建校時！？那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概三十歲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按人的年齡來說的話 大概有130多歲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是成了狗又了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:27.13,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,註：neta自貓又 活了很久尾巴分叉的貓妖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那種東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就交給我吧！好了 快到裡面去！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的 一六你還真是喜歡狗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好乖好乖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.53,0:14:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好棒呢 好乖好乖好乖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}教授的眉毛這裡 不知道怎麼說 還怎是可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有名牌 但是應該是這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.96,0:14:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 為什麼會知道我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好癢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大聲 誰都會知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那也就是說 他記得我們的聲音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得來探病的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}再見啦 教授
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.93,0:15:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好冷好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.45,0:15:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 他怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 真是密不透風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是開窗通下風比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可疑！這種地方會有小黃書…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了！發現了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一六！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 原來老師喜歡巨乳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風子 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 隨你喜歡怎麼做都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以這樣隨便亂翻 一六！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.74,0:16:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼有趣的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好！摔碎了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一六 很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 布丁掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不要磨啦一六！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是禁忌的櫥櫃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 都倒了！風子救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間都被你搞得一團糟啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.76,0:16:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快樂 多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起正月就要數這個了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這個也能看出對方的性格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是語文老師寄來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊 應該還有些別的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:14.94,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也繼續加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.27,0:17:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是可愛的學生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒費什麼功夫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我沒收到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是聽到那個了吧 那時的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 一六！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那確實可能是我有一點 有一點點不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得差別對待是不對的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.14,0:17:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要說一說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:18:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？老師不在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎麼辦 既然都到這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方睡覺的話 感冒會變得更嚴重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.41,0:18:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的老師也會用我們來射擊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 都是因為一六說些奇怪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開槍！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FNC你又來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在煮粥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能光吃泡麵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能隨便進到房間裡來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是之前是在那種情況下被趕出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不是槍械嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會覺得水和濕氣很難應付嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.89,0:19:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師你真是什麼都不懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是軍用槍支哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:20:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨水和鏽跡對我們是沒用的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是對你們的事情一無所知啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.49,0:20:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我們到現在為止也還不知道老師的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.27,0:20:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 重新對您說一次 新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.61,0:20:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 是正月吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在比利時的話 元旦也屬於聖誕節期間哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望至少能夠體會一下正月的氛圍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你啊 但是為什麼要這麼關心我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.66,0:20:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕節和正月都自己一個人的話 不覺得很寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在比利時 聖誕夜大家都聚集在教堂裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉行聖誕節的彌撒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.84,0:20:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讚美歌和管弦樂的聲音會靜靜地響起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.93,0:21:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 但是 今後再多多學習就是了 我們互相之間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FNC
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.76,0:21:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.22,0:21:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到了你很多照顧 猶豫了好久該給你寫些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:27.45,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性格活潑朋友多，讓教室的氣氛都變得明快起來是非常棒的事情。\N而且還會主動幫助老師。但是也有很過份的一面要注意。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要要注意健康哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,0:21:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是穿的是丁字褲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.86,0:21:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是丁字褲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是丁字褲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是丁字褲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.99,0:21:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是丁……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.10,0:21:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風子 語文老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.60,0:21:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.23,0:21:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了啊
