Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.96,0:23:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒打中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.22,0:23:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪老師自己亂生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.97,0:23:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到學園祭啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.41,0:23:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這和一般的學園祭有些不同
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.30,0:23:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要驚訝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.63,0:23:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.25,0:23:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀光 責罵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.49,0:23:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看哦
